{
  "appId": "google_calendar",
  "name": "Google Calendar",
  "version": "0.1.0",
  "type": "integration",
  "description": "Google Calendar integration with per-user, per-calendar sync. Owns calendar data (calendars, events, attendees, attachments). Consumer apps read via the collections API.",
  "crons": [{
    "name": "sync",
    "schedule": "*/5 * * * *",
    "payload": { "type": "sync_all" },
    "overlapPolicy": "skip"
  }],
  "configSchema": {
    "type": "object",
    "properties": {
      "clientId": { "type": "string", "description": "Google OAuth 2.0 Client ID", "platformSecret": "GOOGLE_CALENDAR_CLIENT_ID" },
      "clientSecret": { "type": "string", "description": "Google OAuth 2.0 Client Secret", "platformSecret": "GOOGLE_CALENDAR_CLIENT_SECRET" }
    },
    "required": ["clientId", "clientSecret"]
  },
  "userAuth": { "type": "redirect" },
  "actions": [
    {
      "id": "sync_connect",
      "name": "Start Sync",
      "description": "Initialize sync for the current user. Lists user calendars (selected only), creates one sync_cursor per calendar, registers a 5-min cron, triggers the first sync.",
      "inputSchema": { "type": "object" },
      "outputSchema": { "type": "object", "properties": { "cursor_ids": { "type": "array", "items": { "type": "string" } }, "calendars": { "type": "array" } } }
    },
    {
      "id": "sync_disconnect",
      "name": "Stop Sync",
      "description": "Disable sync for the current user. Removes cron, keeps synced data.",
      "inputSchema": { "type": "object" },
      "outputSchema": { "type": "object", "properties": { "ok": { "type": "boolean" } } }
    },
    {
      "id": "sync_now",
      "name": "Trigger Sync",
      "description": "Trigger an immediate sync for the current user.",
      "inputSchema": { "type": "object" },
      "outputSchema": { "type": "object", "properties": { "triggered": { "type": "boolean" } } }
    },
    {
      "id": "get_profile",
      "name": "Get Profile",
      "description": "Return the user's primary email and timezone.",
      "inputSchema": { "type": "object" },
      "outputSchema": { "type": "object", "properties": { "emailAddress": { "type": "string" }, "timeZone": { "type": "string" } } }
    },
    {
      "id": "list_calendars",
      "name": "List Calendars",
      "description": "List the user's calendars (calendarList).",
      "inputSchema": { "type": "object", "properties": { "showHidden": { "type": "boolean" }, "minAccessRole": { "type": "string", "enum": ["freeBusyReader", "reader", "writer", "owner"] } } },
      "outputSchema": { "type": "object", "properties": { "calendars": { "type": "array" } } }
    },
    {
      "id": "update_calendar_visibility",
      "name": "Update Calendar Visibility",
      "description": "Set the visibility of one of the user's synced calendars. share_everything makes event titles and descriptions visible to all workspace users; metadata only shows times and a 'Not shared' placeholder.",
      "inputSchema": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "calendarExternalId": { "type": "string" },
          "visibility": { "type": "string", "enum": ["share_everything", "metadata"] }
        },
        "required": ["calendarExternalId", "visibility"]
      },
      "outputSchema": { "type": "object", "properties": { "ok": { "type": "boolean" } } }
    },
    {
      "id": "list_events",
      "name": "List Events",
      "description": "List events for a calendar. Either pass a time window (timeMin/timeMax/q/orderBy) for fresh queries, or a syncToken for incremental sync. syncToken is mutually exclusive with timeMin/timeMax/q/orderBy.",
      "inputSchema": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "calendarId": { "type": "string" },
          "timeMin": { "type": "string" },
          "timeMax": { "type": "string" },
          "q": { "type": "string" },
          "maxResults": { "type": "integer" },
          "pageToken": { "type": "string" },
          "singleEvents": { "type": "boolean" },
          "showDeleted": { "type": "boolean" },
          "orderBy": { "type": "string", "enum": ["startTime", "updated"] },
          "syncToken": { "type": "string" }
        }
      },
      "outputSchema": { "type": "object", "properties": { "events": { "type": "array" }, "nextPageToken": { "type": "string" }, "nextSyncToken": { "type": "string" } } }
    },
    {
      "id": "get_event",
      "name": "Get Event",
      "description": "Get a single event by ID.",
      "inputSchema": { "type": "object", "properties": { "calendarId": { "type": "string" }, "eventId": { "type": "string" } }, "required": ["eventId"] },
      "outputSchema": { "type": "object" }
    },
    {
      "id": "create_event",
      "name": "Create Event",
      "description": "Create an event. Supports attendees, RRULE, all-day, and optional Google Meet creation.",
      "inputSchema": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "calendarId": { "type": "string", "description": "Default: primary" },
          "summary": { "type": "string" },
          "description": { "type": "string" },
          "location": { "type": "string" },
          "start": { "type": "object", "description": "{ dateTime, timeZone } or { date }" },
          "end": { "type": "object", "description": "{ dateTime, timeZone } or { date }" },
          "attendees": { "type": "array", "items": { "type": "object", "properties": { "email": { "type": "string" }, "displayName": { "type": "string" }, "optional": { "type": "boolean" } }, "required": ["email"] } },
          "recurrence": { "type": "array", "items": { "type": "string" }, "description": "RFC5545 RRULE/RDATE/EXDATE lines" },
          "createMeet": { "type": "boolean", "default": false, "description": "If true, request an auto-generated Google Meet conference" },
          "sendUpdates": { "type": "string", "enum": ["all", "externalOnly", "none"], "default": "all" },
          "guestsCanModify": { "type": "boolean" },
          "guestsCanInviteOthers": { "type": "boolean" },
          "transparency": { "type": "string", "enum": ["opaque", "transparent"] },
          "visibility": { "type": "string", "enum": ["default", "public", "private", "confidential"] }
        },
        "required": ["summary", "start", "end"]
      },
      "outputSchema": { "type": "object", "properties": { "eventId": { "type": "string" }, "htmlLink": { "type": "string" }, "hangoutLink": { "type": "string" } } }
    },
    {
      "id": "update_event",
      "name": "Update Event",
      "description": "Patch an event (partial update).",
      "inputSchema": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "calendarId": { "type": "string" },
          "eventId": { "type": "string" },
          "patch": { "type": "object" },
          "sendUpdates": { "type": "string", "enum": ["all", "externalOnly", "none"], "default": "all" }
        },
        "required": ["eventId", "patch"]
      },
      "outputSchema": { "type": "object" }
    },
    {
      "id": "delete_event",
      "name": "Delete Event",
      "description": "Delete an event.",
      "inputSchema": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "calendarId": { "type": "string" },
          "eventId": { "type": "string" },
          "sendUpdates": { "type": "string", "enum": ["all", "externalOnly", "none"], "default": "all" }
        },
        "required": ["eventId"]
      },
      "outputSchema": { "type": "object", "properties": { "ok": { "type": "boolean" } } }
    },
    {
      "id": "respond_event",
      "name": "Respond to Event",
      "description": "Set the current user's responseStatus on an event (accepted/declined/tentative).",
      "inputSchema": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "calendarId": { "type": "string" },
          "eventId": { "type": "string" },
          "responseStatus": { "type": "string", "enum": ["accepted", "declined", "tentative", "needsAction"] }
        },
        "required": ["eventId", "responseStatus"]
      },
      "outputSchema": { "type": "object" }
    },
    {
      "id": "quick_add",
      "name": "Quick Add Event",
      "description": "Create an event from natural-language text (events.quickAdd).",
      "inputSchema": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "calendarId": { "type": "string" },
          "text": { "type": "string" },
          "sendUpdates": { "type": "string", "enum": ["all", "externalOnly", "none"], "default": "all" }
        },
        "required": ["text"]
      },
      "outputSchema": { "type": "object", "properties": { "eventId": { "type": "string" } } }
    },
    {
      "id": "freebusy",
      "name": "Free/Busy",
      "description": "Query availability for up to 50 calendars within a time window.",
      "inputSchema": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "timeMin": { "type": "string" },
          "timeMax": { "type": "string" },
          "items": { "type": "array", "items": { "type": "object", "properties": { "id": { "type": "string" } }, "required": ["id"] } },
          "timeZone": { "type": "string" }
        },
        "required": ["timeMin", "timeMax", "items"]
      },
      "outputSchema": { "type": "object", "properties": { "calendars": { "type": "object" } } }
    },
    {
      "id": "watch",
      "name": "Watch Calendar",
      "description": "Register a push notification channel for an events list (manual; not used by default cron).",
      "inputSchema": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "calendarId": { "type": "string" },
          "address": { "type": "string" },
          "token": { "type": "string" },
          "ttlSeconds": { "type": "integer" }
        },
        "required": ["address"]
      },
      "outputSchema": { "type": "object", "properties": { "channelId": { "type": "string" }, "resourceId": { "type": "string" }, "expiration": { "type": "integer" } } }
    },
    {
      "id": "stop_watch",
      "name": "Stop Watch",
      "description": "Terminate a previously registered push channel.",
      "inputSchema": { "type": "object", "properties": { "channelId": { "type": "string" }, "resourceId": { "type": "string" } }, "required": ["channelId", "resourceId"] },
      "outputSchema": { "type": "object" }
    }
  ],
  "dataContract": [
    {
      "entityName": "calendars",
      "fields": [
        { "name": "external_id",   "type": "text", "required": true },
        { "name": "user_id",       "type": "text", "required": true },
        { "name": "summary",       "type": "text" },
        { "name": "description",   "type": "text" },
        { "name": "primary",       "type": "boolean" },
        { "name": "time_zone",     "type": "text" },
        { "name": "access_role",   "type": "text" },
        { "name": "background_color", "type": "text" },
        { "name": "foreground_color", "type": "text" },
        { "name": "selected",      "type": "boolean" },
        { "name": "visibility",    "type": "text", "enum_values": ["share_everything", "metadata"] }
      ]
    },
    {
      "entityName": "events",
      "fields": [
        { "name": "external_id",          "type": "text", "required": true },
        { "name": "ical_uid",             "type": "text" },
        { "name": "title",                "type": "text" },
        { "name": "description",          "type": "text" },
        { "name": "location",             "type": "text" },
        { "name": "starts_at",            "type": "timestamp" },
        { "name": "ends_at",              "type": "timestamp" },
        { "name": "is_full_day",          "type": "boolean" },
        { "name": "time_zone",            "type": "text" },
        { "name": "external_created_at",  "type": "timestamp" },
        { "name": "external_updated_at",  "type": "timestamp" },
        { "name": "recurring_event_external_id", "type": "text" },
        { "name": "recurrence",           "type": "text" },
        { "name": "conference_solution",  "type": "text" },
        { "name": "conference_link",      "type": "text" },
        { "name": "html_link",            "type": "text" },
        { "name": "organizer_address",    "type": "text" },
        { "name": "transparency",         "type": "text" },
        { "name": "visibility",           "type": "text" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "entityName": "channel_event_associations",
      "fields": [
        { "name": "event_id",                "type": "entity_link", "onDelete": "cascade", "references": { "entity": "events", "field": "id" }, "required": true },
        { "name": "user_id",                 "type": "text", "required": true },
        { "name": "calendar_external_id",    "type": "text", "required": true },
        { "name": "event_external_id",       "type": "text", "required": true },
        { "name": "recurring_event_external_id", "type": "text" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "entityName": "attendees",
      "fields": [
        { "name": "event_id",        "type": "entity_link", "onDelete": "cascade", "references": { "entity": "events", "field": "id" }, "required": true },
        { "name": "address",         "type": "text", "required": true },
        { "name": "display_name",    "type": "text" },
        { "name": "response_status", "type": "text", "enum_values": ["needs_action", "declined", "tentative", "accepted"] },
        { "name": "is_organizer",    "type": "boolean" },
        { "name": "optional",        "type": "boolean" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "entityName": "event_attachments",
      "fields": [
        { "name": "event_id",   "type": "entity_link", "onDelete": "cascade", "references": { "entity": "events", "field": "id" }, "required": true },
        { "name": "file_id",    "type": "text" },
        { "name": "file_url",   "type": "text" },
        { "name": "title",      "type": "text" },
        { "name": "mime_type",  "type": "text" },
        { "name": "icon_link",  "type": "text" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "entityName": "sync_cursors",
      "fields": [
        { "name": "user_id",              "type": "text", "required": true },
        { "name": "calendar_external_id", "type": "text", "required": true },
        { "name": "sync_token",           "type": "text" },
        { "name": "status",               "type": "text", "enum_values": ["idle", "syncing", "needs_reauth", "failed_temporary", "failed_permanent"] },
        { "name": "last_synced_at",       "type": "timestamp" },
        { "name": "throttle_count",       "type": "number" },
        { "name": "throttle_after",       "type": "timestamp" },
        { "name": "cron_id",              "type": "text" },
        { "name": "watch_channel_id",     "type": "text" },
        { "name": "watch_resource_id",    "type": "text" },
        { "name": "watch_expires_at",     "type": "timestamp" },
        { "name": "enabled",              "type": "boolean" }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "permissions": {
    "permissions": [
      { "key": "calendars.read",   "description": "Read synced calendars" },
      { "key": "calendars.write",  "description": "Write calendars (internal sync)" },
      { "key": "events.read",      "description": "Read synced events" },
      { "key": "events.write",     "description": "Write events (internal sync)" },
      { "key": "channel_event_associations.read",  "description": "Read calendar/event associations" },
      { "key": "channel_event_associations.write", "description": "Write associations (internal sync)" },
      { "key": "attendees.read",   "description": "Read event attendees" },
      { "key": "attendees.write",  "description": "Write attendees (internal sync)" },
      { "key": "event_attachments.read",  "description": "Read event attachment metadata" },
      { "key": "event_attachments.write", "description": "Write attachments (internal sync)" },
      { "key": "sync_cursors.read",  "description": "Read sync state" },
      { "key": "sync_cursors.write", "description": "Manage sync state" }
    ]
  },
  "instructions": "Google Calendar integration v0.1 -- owns calendar data.\n\nThis integration syncs events from all user-selected calendars (calendarList where selected=true) and stores them in its own entities. Consumer apps (CRM, scheduler) read via the collections API:\n\n  GET /api/v1/apps/google_calendar/collections/events?where={...}\n  GET /api/v1/apps/google_calendar/collections/attendees?where={address: {$eq: \"user@example.com\"}}\n\nSync model:\n- One sync_cursor per (user_id, calendar_external_id)\n- syncToken per calendar (incremental). 410 Gone -> reset to full sync.\n- singleEvents=true everywhere (recurring instances flattened)\n- showDeleted=true is required by syncToken; cancelled events trigger DELETE locally\n- Cron 5min loops over enabled cursors, calls events.list with syncToken\n\nDedup:\n- events.ical_uid is UNIQUE -> same event invited to multiple synced accounts/calendars is stored once\n- channel_event_associations is N:M between event and (user, calendar)\n\nWrite actions:\n- create_event: pass createMeet=true to auto-generate a Google Meet (sets conferenceDataVersion=1)\n- update_event/delete_event/respond_event: sendUpdates defaults to 'all'\n- quick_add: natural-language event creation (events.quickAdd)\n\nFreeBusy:\n- Up to 50 calendars per query\n\nError contract (mirrors Gmail integration):\n- All actions return {ok: true, data} or {ok: false, error: {code, message, retryAfter?}}\n- Codes: INSUFFICIENT_PERMISSIONS, TEMPORARY_ERROR, SYNC_CURSOR_ERROR, NOT_FOUND, MISCONFIGURED, UNKNOWN"
}
